title: Live NRL trial: Warriors v Titans
text:
Live NRL trial: Warriors v Gold Coast Titans scores, updates, news, blog  34am Source: FOX SPORTS COMBINATIONS will be put to the test when the Warriors take on the Gold Coast Titans in New Zealand in a pre-season trial match. 
Young Titans halves Ash Taylor and Kane Elgey will play together for the first time, while Tyrone Roberts will deputise at fullback for Jarryd Hayne. 
Flyers Anthony Don, Will Zillman, Daniel Vidot and Tyronne Roberts-Davis will all shoot out for round one wing spots. 
LIVE stream NZ Warriors v Gold Coast Titans Trial Game on FOX SPORTS. Get your free 2-week FOXTEL PLAY trial and start watching in minutes. SIGN UP NOW > 
Meanwhile, Warriors fullback Roger Tuivasa-Sheck will play his second game since returning from a serious knee injury. 
The match kicks off at 12:00pm (AEDT). 
Follow all the action in the live blog below!
